    <section class="section-faqs-main">
        <h1 class="head-">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
        <p>Find answers to the most common questions about YourRide’s self-drive and chauffeur-driven car rental
            services across Pakistan.</p>
            <section class="section-faqs">
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>What documents do I need to rent a car?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            For self-drive rentals, you need a valid CNIC (Computerized National Identity Card), a valid driving
                            license with at least one year of experience, and you must be at least 21 years old. A security
                            deposit
                            is also required. For chauffeur-driven services, you only need valid identification.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>How do I book a car rental?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            You can book a car rental by submitting an inquiry through our website form, contacting us via
                            WhatsApp,
                            or calling our customer service. We'll confirm availability, pricing, and guide you through the
                            process.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>What is included in the rental price?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            The rental price includes the vehicle, basic insurance, and 24/7 roadside assistance. Fuel, tolls,
                            parking, and extra services are charged separately.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Can I rent a car for just a few hours?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, we offer hourly, daily, weekly, and monthly rentals. Minimum rental period usually starts from
                            4 hours for self-drive cars.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>What happens if the car breaks down?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            All vehicles are regularly serviced. In case of an issue, we provide 24/7 roadside assistance and
                            replacement support if required.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Do you provide insurance?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, basic insurance coverage is included with all rentals. This covers standard liability and
                            vehicle
                            damage. Additional comprehensive coverage options are available for purchase.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Can I drive the car to other cities?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, you can drive our rental vehicles to other cities within Pakistan. Please inform us during
                            booking
                            as additional terms may apply.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>What is your cancellation policy?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Cancellations made 24–48 hours before rental usually receive a refund. Last-minute cancellations may
                            incur charges.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Are your drivers professional and experienced?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, all our chauffeurs are trained professionals with strong local knowledge and a commitment to
                            safety and service.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Do you offer airport pickup and drop-off?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, we provide airport pickup and drop-off services at major airports across Pakistan with flight
                            monitoring support.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>
                        <p>Can I extend my rental period?</p>
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-arrow-down"></i>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-content">
                        <p>
                            Yes, extensions are possible depending on availability. Please inform us as early as possible.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
        
            </section>

    </section>